text: Hello Jane. sorry for the late reply. work is very busy given all the Coronavirus things happening.  I really like the additional images and working you are adding to your portfolio.  I think it's great to show how you think and get to your end result.
On another note I hope you and your family are well and safe.
Good luck with your interview.  I hope it goes really well. You are prepared and have some lovely work to show with a good narrative as to how you created it and why. :slightly_smiling_face:
No worries, I understand since it's the same over here with schools shutting and everything being disrupted. Please stay safe too
